    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://newyork.craigslist.org/que/fbh/6044804987.html"></div>
        </div>
Outdoor / Indoor Venue in Astoria is seeking experienced, dynamic professional for the position of General Manager. <br>
<br>
Candidate will be responsible for overseeing all operational parts of the business, including but not limited to: bar and restaurant operations, event and banquet operations, yearly budget projections and forecasts including labor, food and beverage cost review and reporting. Manager will control purchases and inventory, negotiate prices and contracts, review usage reports and take corrective actions. General Manager will follow through on financial objectives, analyze variances; establish and monitor financial controls; develop and implement strategies to increase annual revenue. This position includes the responsibility for the acquisition/maintenance of all licenses, permits, fee payments and other official requirements pertaining to food, beverage and all business operations to ensure a continuous and uninterrupted operation. This position also includes maintaining a safe, secure and healthy facility environment by enforcing sanitation standards and procedures, complying with health and legal regulations and upholding professional knowledge by tracking emerging trends in the restaurant industry. <br>
This is a Full-Time position. Competitive salary based on experience. Compensation may be negotiable for the right candidate.<br>
Resumes should be sent to: gm.bcbsa@gmail.com<br>
    </section>

